If the GM believes I‚Äôve engaged in fraud‚Äîand that I falsified my browser history‚Äîhe should at least have the cojones to explain it to me in an email. Cowardice is not a good look!/8

@MarriottRewards @MarriottBonvoy @JWMarriott @MBonvoyAssist @FairfieldHotels @JoshuaTreeNPS @BestWestern @acehotel But that‚Äôs not why I‚Äôve resorted to Twitter. I‚Äôm here b/c after I sent the #FairfieldInns GM my screen-shot, he responded by saying I had a reservation for 11/27, not 11/28. And when I sent him the email proving the reservation was for 11/28, he stopped responding. GHOSTED! /7

@MarriottRewards @MarriottBonvoy @JWMarriott @MBonvoyAssist @FairfieldHotels @JoshuaTreeNPS @BestWestern @acehotel So the #FairfieldInns GM is implicitly accusing me of falsifying my browser history or failing to cancel my reservation before staying elsewhere the same night; I‚Äôm either a fraud or irresponsible! (Or maybe he thinks I tried to cancel but goofed; if so, he has no compassion.) /6

@MarriottRewards @MarriottBonvoy @JWMarriott @MBonvoyAssist @FairfieldHotels @JoshuaTreeNPS @BestWestern @acehotel But that‚Äôs evidence that I cancelled. Sure, it‚Äôs not dispositive; I could have gone to the cancellation page and decided NOT to cancel. But the browser history ALSO shows I went to @BestWestern‚Äôs website NEXT. And I can PROVE I stayed at #BestWestern the night on 11/28. /5

@MarriottRewards @MarriottBonvoy @JWMarriott @MBonvoyAssist @FairfieldHotels @JoshuaTreeNPS @BestWestern @acehotel So #FairfieldInns charged me for 11/28. When I requested a refund, the hotel‚Äôs GM gave me half my $ as a ‚Äúcourtesy,‚Äù saying I had no evidence I cancelled. So I sent him a screen-shot of my browser history, PROVING I went to the cancellation page on the eve of 11/26. No dice! /4

@MarriottRewards @MarriottBonvoy @JWMarriott @MBonvoyAssist @FairfieldHotels @JoshuaTreeNPS @BestWestern @acehotel Since I was on my phone, I didn‚Äôt print a PDF of my confirmation, as I usually do; sadly, it did not occur to me to screenshot it. I then made my #BestWestern reservation for the same nite. Next day, I get an email from #FairfieldInns: they had not learned of my cancellation! /3
